Good:
Cold pressed or expeller pressed sesame oil, sunflower oil, peanut oil, macadamia oil, avocado oil, flax oil and high
oleic safflower oil in small amounts; refined palm oil;
refined coconut oil; filtered extra virgin olive oil.

Best:
Organic raw vinegars; organic aged balsamic vinegars; raw naturally fermented soy sauce, tamari and miso; arrowroot;
mustard made with natural ingredients; flavoring mixes
made with natural ingredients; organic mirin.

Avoid:
Most canned and all dehydrated soups, which
are loaded with MSG; stock sold in aseptic boxes;
bouillon cubes.
